SENSEEVIL: Detect evil in the room

Syntax: senseevil
        psi sense evil

DESCRIPTION:
  Detect evil presences in the current room. Costs 2 ISP. No save.

NOTES:
  You must know sense evil and have enough ISP.
  In combat, using psionics costs one attack from your APM pool.

SEE ALSO: psi, psionics
